snippet.title: Ambrosia: Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
A storm of white-hot gunfire. A single shattering bullet. Or a cataclysm of photons. The choice is yours in Ambrosia! Customize your arsenal with rule-based, game-changing mods to overcome Aspida's ruthless foes in this futurepunk explore 'em up.

For more info, check us out at https://ambrosia.realmsoft.com/, or hit up our social media accounts!

Twitter: https://twitter.com/realmsoftdevs
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/realmsoftdevs/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/realmsoft/
